info.author: peyman (peter)
info.description:
foxmemo is gui-based form development tool over the web with no programming
required. foxmemo is based on qooxdoo (ajax framework) on the front end. On the
back-end side, foxmemo relies on python, postgresql and karrigell (web server).

To some degree, it resembles django; but without coding!
